Summarize MizerSim object

Source: R/summary_methods.R
summary-MizerSim-method.Rd

Outputs a general summary of the structure and content of the object

# S4 method for MizerSim
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

A MizerSim object.
...

Other arguments (currently not used).

Examples

summary(NS_sim)
